#: ../../skill_guide.md:1
msgid "Skill 编写指南"
msgstr "Skill Authoring Guide"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:3
msgid ""
"本文档介绍如何为 `PersonAgent` 编写自定义 Skill。Skill "
"的目标不是把所有逻辑写成复杂插件，而是把一种能力的触发条件、输入文件、执行步骤和输出文件说明清楚，让智能体在合适的时候调用它。"
msgstr ""
"This document describes how to write a custom Skill for `PersonAgent`. The "
"goal of Skill is not to write all logic as complex plug-ins, but to clearly "
"explain the trigger conditions, input files, execution steps and output "
"files of a capability so that the agent can call it at the appropriate time."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:5
msgid "概述"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:7
msgid "Skill 是 `PersonAgent` 的行为模块。常见写法有两种："
msgstr ""
"Skill is `PersonAgent`’s behavioral module. There are two common ways of "
"writing:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:9
msgid "**Prompt-only**：只写 `SKILL.md`，适合判断、反思、总结、计划等开放任务。"
msgstr ""
"**Prompt-only**: Only write `SKILL.md`, suitable for open tasks such as "
"judgment, reflection, summary, and planning."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:10
msgid "**Subprocess script**：额外提供 Python 脚本，适合确定性计算、格式转换、批处理和可重复的数据维护。"
msgstr ""
"**Subprocess script**: Additional Python scripts are provided, suitable for "
"deterministic calculations, format conversion, batch processing and "
"repeatable data maintenance."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:12
msgid "与环境交互时，不需要在 frontmatter 里声明特殊 executor；在正文中说明何时使用 `codegen` 工具即可。"
msgstr ""
"When interacting with the environment, there is no need to declare a special"
" executor in the frontmatter; just explain in the text when to use the "
"`codegen` tool."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:14
msgid "快速开始"
msgstr "Quick Start"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:16
msgid "创建一个简单的Skill"
msgstr "Create a simple Skill"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:18
msgid "在`custom/skills/`目录下创建新文件夹："
msgstr "Create a new folder in the `custom/skills/` directory:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:25
msgid "编写SKILL.md："
msgstr "Write SKILL.md:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:71
msgid "无需编程，模型会根据你的描述读取文件、调用工具并写入输出。写得越具体，行为越稳定。"
msgstr ""
"No programming required, the model reads files, calls tools, and writes "
"output based on your description. The more specific it is written, the more "
"stable the behavior will be."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:73
msgid "SKILL.md结构详解"
msgstr "Detailed explanation of SKILL.md structure"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:75
msgid "Frontmatter（必需）"
msgstr "Frontmatter (required)"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:77
msgid "Frontmatter是YAML格式的元数据块，位于文件开头："
msgstr ""
"Frontmatter is a YAML formatted metadata block located at the beginning of "
"the file:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:86
msgid ""
"可选：在同目录下放置 ``scripts/<name>.py``，运行时会作为子进程脚本执行；依赖关系写在正文里，由模型按需 "
"``activate_skill``。"
msgstr ""
"Optional: Place ``scripts/<name>.py`` in the same directory, and it will be "
"executed as a sub-process script when running; dependencies are written in "
"the text, and ``activate_skill`` is determined by the model on demand."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:88
msgid "Body（必需）"
msgstr "Body (required)"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:90
msgid "Body是Markdown格式的行为指南，告诉LLM："
msgstr "Body is a Markdown-formatted behavioral guide that tells LLM:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:92
msgid "**何时使用**：触发条件"
msgstr "**何时使用**: Trigger condition"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:93
msgid "**输入**：读取哪些文件"
msgstr "**输入**: Which files to read"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:94
msgid "**做什么**：执行步骤"
msgstr "**做什么**: Execution steps"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:95
msgid "**输出**：产生什么文件"
msgstr "**输出**: What file is generated?"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:97
msgid "可用的内置工具"
msgstr "Available built-in tools"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:99
msgid "Skill的Markdown body中可以指导LLM使用以下工具："
msgstr ""
"The Markdown body of the Skill can instruct LLM to use the following tools:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "工具"
msgstr "Tool"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "用途"
msgstr "Usage"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "示例"
msgstr "Examples"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`workspace_read`"
msgstr "`workspace_read`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "读取文件"
msgstr "Read file"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`workspace_read(\"state/observation.txt\")`"
msgstr "`workspace_read(\"state/observation.txt\")`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`workspace_write`"
msgstr "`workspace_write`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "写入文件"
msgstr "Write file"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`workspace_write(\"state/result.json\", content)`"
msgstr "`workspace_write(\"state/result.json\", content)`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`workspace_list`"
msgstr "`workspace_list`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "列出文件"
msgstr "List files"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`workspace_list(\".\")`"
msgstr "`workspace_list(\".\")`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`codegen`"
msgstr "`codegen`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "执行环境指令"
msgstr "Execute environment instructions"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`codegen(\"<observe>\")`"
msgstr "`codegen(\"<observe>\")`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`bash`"
msgstr "`bash`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "执行命令"
msgstr "Execute command"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`bash(\"echo hello\")`"
msgstr "`bash(\"echo hello\")`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`grep`"
msgstr "`grep`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "搜索内容"
msgstr "Search content"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`grep(\"pattern\", \".\")`"
msgstr "`grep(\"pattern\", \".\")`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`glob`"
msgstr "`glob`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "文件匹配"
msgstr "File matching"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`glob(\"*.json\")`"
msgstr "`glob(\"*.json\")`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "`done`"
msgstr "`done`"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "完成执行"
msgstr "Finish execution"

#: ../../skill_guide.md
msgid "表示skill执行完毕"
msgstr "Indicates that the skill execution is complete"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:112
msgid "Skill类型"
msgstr "Skill type"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:114
msgid "类型1：纯Prompt驱动（推荐）"
msgstr "Type 1: Pure prompt-driven (recommended)"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:116
msgid "大多数Skill不需要编程，只需要清晰的描述："
msgstr "Most skills do not require programming, just clear description:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:144
msgid "类型2：带Python脚本"
msgstr "Type 2: With Python script"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:146
msgid "当需要确定性计算时，添加Python脚本："
msgstr "When deterministic calculations are required, add a Python script:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:155
msgid "SKILL.md:"
msgstr "SKILL.md:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:164
msgid "calc.py:"
msgstr "calc.py:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:198 ../../skill_guide.md:380
msgid "与环境交互"
msgstr "Interact with the environment"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:200
msgid ""
"在 SKILL 正文里说明何时调用内置 **`codegen`** 工具即可；不要在 frontmatter 里写 "
"``executor``（框架不解析）。"
msgstr ""
"Just state in the SKILL body when to call the built-in **`codegen`** tool; "
"do not write ``executor`` in the frontmatter (the framework will not parse "
"it)."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:202
msgid "最佳实践"
msgstr "Best practices"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:204
msgid "1. 保持单一职责"
msgstr "1. Maintain a single responsibility"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:206
msgid "每个 Skill 只做一件事："
msgstr "Each Skill only does one thing:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:208
msgid "✅ `cognition`: 生成情绪和意图"
msgstr "✅ `cognition`: Generate emotions and intentions"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:209
msgid "✅ `memory`: 写入值得长期保留的记忆"
msgstr "✅ `memory`: Write memories worthy of long-term retention"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:210
msgid "❌ `needs_and_emotion`: 做太多事情"
msgstr "❌ `needs_and_emotion`: Doing too many things"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:212
msgid "2. 在正文写清产出文件"
msgstr "2. Write the output file clearly in the text"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:214
msgid ""
"在 Markdown 里列出会写入的路径（如 ``state/result.json``）；frontmatter 不解析 "
"``outputs``、``inputs``、``requires`` 等扩展字段。"
msgstr ""
"List the paths that will be written in Markdown (such as "
"``state/result.json``); frontmatter does not parse extension fields such as "
"``outputs``, ``inputs``, ``requires``, etc."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:216
msgid "3. 处理缺失文件"
msgstr "3. Handle missing files"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:218
msgid "Skill应该优雅处理输入文件不存在的情况："
msgstr ""
"The skill should handle gracefully the case where the input file does not "
"exist:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:226
msgid "4. 提供示例"
msgstr "4. Provide examples"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:228
msgid "示例帮助LLM理解预期行为："
msgstr "Examples help LLM understand expected behavior:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:248
msgid "5. 避免冗余描述"
msgstr "5. Avoid redundant descriptions"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:250
msgid "不需要告诉LLM\"仔细思考\"或\"认真分析\"，它会自然地做这些。"
msgstr ""
"There is no need to tell LLM to \"think carefully\" or \"analyze "
"carefully\", it will do this naturally."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:252
msgid "文件结构约定"
msgstr "File structure convention"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:254
msgid "推荐使用以下目录结构："
msgstr "It is recommended to use the following directory structure:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:267
msgid "调试技巧"
msgstr "Debugging Tips"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:269
msgid "**查看workspace文件**：检查输出文件是否正确生成"
msgstr ""
"**Check workspace files**: Check whether the output file is generated correctly"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:270
msgid "**检查tool_calls.jsonl**：查看LLM调用了哪些工具"
msgstr "**Check tool_calls.jsonl**: Check which tools are called by LLM"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:271
msgid "**简化描述**：如果Skill行为异常，尝试简化描述"
msgstr ""
"**Simplify description**: If the Skill behaves abnormally, try to simplify "
"the description"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:272
msgid "**添加示例**：示例通常能显著改善LLM理解"
msgstr "**Add examples**: Examples often significantly improve LLM understanding"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:274
msgid "示例：完整的Skill"
msgstr "Example: Complete Skill"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:348
msgid "常见问题"
msgstr "FAQ"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:350
msgid "**Q: Skill之间如何通信？**"
msgstr "**Q: How do Skills communicate with each other?**"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:352
msgid "A: 通过workspace文件。一个Skill写入文件，另一个Skill读取。"
msgstr ""
"A: Through the workspace file. One Skill writes to the file and another "
"Skill reads."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:354
msgid "**Q: 如何控制Skill执行顺序？**"
msgstr "**Q: How to control Skill execution order?**"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:356
msgid ""
"A: 由主模型在工具循环里决定先 ``activate_skill`` 哪一个；若有硬依赖，在 SKILL.md 正文写清并引导先激活依赖 skill。"
msgstr ""
"A: The main model decides which ``activate_skill`` to use first in the tool "
"loop; if there is a hard dependency, write it clearly in the SKILL.md text "
"and guide the dependent skill to be activated first."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:358
msgid "**Q: Skill可以调用其他Skill吗？**"
msgstr "**Q: Can a Skill call other Skills?**"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:360
msgid "A: 不直接调用。通过workspace文件松耦合，LLM决定何时激活哪个Skill。"
msgstr ""
"A: Not called directly. Loosely coupled through workspace files, LLM decides"
" when to activate which Skill."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:362
msgid "**Q: 如何测试Skill？**"
msgstr "**Q: How to test a Skill?**"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:364
msgid "A: 创建测试workspace，放置输入文件，运行agent，检查输出文件。"
msgstr ""
"A: Create a test workspace, place input files, run the agent, and check the "
"output files."

